data.description: Nestled in the heart of the City of St. Joseph, this delightful property presents the opportunity to embrace comfortable living in a prime location. With its charming curb appeal and inviting ambiance, this home is sure to capture your heart.  Conveniently situated across from St. Joseph High School and in close proximity to Downtown St. Joseph and the Beaches.  Step inside and enjoy the abundant natural light in the living room, which is complimented with a cozy wood burning fireplace.  You will also be pleased by the abundance of space and storage with 3 bedrooms, including an upper level bedroom/office/playroom as well as a semi-finished basement, ideal for an extra living area (and plenty of room for storage!)  Come see the potential to make this into your ideal next home!
